whole_object: Looks like the city planners were really thinking ahead – they built a skyscraper that's the perfect size for a giant's game of ring toss!
single_object:
- Tree: "I'm rooting for you to grow tall and branch out!"
- Streetlight: "I’m just here to brighten your day, one bulb at a time!"
- Building: "I’m not just a structure; I’m a skyscraper of dreams!"
- Van: "I’m not just a vehicle; I’m a mobile adventure waiting to happen!"
- Bicycle: "I’m two-tired of standing still; let’s pedal to the metal!"
- Traffic light: "I’m the ultimate referee in this game of stop and go!"
- Street sign: "I’m here to point you in the right direction, no ifs, ands, or buts!"
- Fence: "I’m just trying to keep my boundaries in check, one picket at a time!"
- Pole: "I’m not just standing around; I’m a support system for all your needs!"
multi_object:
- Tree  
- Streetlight  
- "The tree told the streetlight, 'I’m rooting for you to shine bright, but I’m just here for the shade!'"

- Streetlight  
- Traffic light  
- "The streetlight said to the traffic light, 'You may have the red light, but I’m always in the spotlight!'"

- Building  
- Van  
- "The building looked down at the van and said, 'I may have more stories, but you’ve got the wheels to roll with!'"

- Van  
- Bicycle  
- "The van chuckled at the bicycle, 'I may be bigger, but you’ve got the pedal power to outrun my parking tickets!'"

- Bicycle  
- Fence  
- "The bicycle leaned against the fence and said, 'I may be two-tired, but at least I don’t have to deal with a picket fence!'"

- Traffic light  
- Pole  
- "The traffic light told the pole, 'I’m just here to stop traffic, but you’re really holding it all together!'"

- Street sign  
- Building  
- "The street sign pointed at the building and said, 'I may give directions, but you’ve got the address everyone wants!'"

- Fence  
- Tree  
- "The fence whispered to the tree, 'I may keep things in line, but you’re the one with the roots in the ground!'" 

- Pole  
- Streetlight  
- "The pole joked with the streetlight, 'I’m just here to hold you up, but you’re the one lighting up the night!'"
